{"content": "I need to multiply 252\u2089 \u00d7 580\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n252\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 162 + 45 + 2 = 209\u2081\u2080\n\n580\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 405 + 72 + 0 = 477\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n209 \u00d7 477 = 99,693\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n99693 \u00f7 9 = 11077 r 0\n11077 \u00f7 9 = 1230 r 7\n1230 \u00f7 9 = 136 r 6\n136 \u00f7 9 = 15 r 1\n15 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 6\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **161670\u2089**\n\n161670", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 325}